\sum_{n=1}^{m}\arctan\left({\frac{1}{{n^2+n+1}}}\right)
\text{arctan}(u)-\text{arctan}(v) = \text{arctan}(\frac{u-v}{1+uv})
u=n+1
v=n
\text{arctan}\left(\frac1{n^2+n+1}\right) = \text{arctan}(n+1)-\text{arctan}(n)
\sum_{n=1}^{m}\arctan\left({\frac{1}{{n^2+n+1}}}\right) = \text{arctan}(m+1) - \pi/4
\tan^{-1}\frac{1}{n^2+n+1}=\cot^{-1}(n^2+n+1)=\cot^{-1}\frac{n(n+1)+1}{n+1-n}
=\cot^{-1}(n)-\cot^{-1}(n+1)
